								<div class="inner">
									<h2><a href="https://www.facebook.com/onyxai" target="_blank">Onyx for Facebook Messenger</a></h2>
									<p>Onyx is a Facebook Messenger chatbot as well. This avatar of the virtual being is built using Node.js and deployed on <a href="https://heroku.com/" target="_blank">Heroku</a>. Needless to say, this is open source and you may find the source code on <a href="https://www.github.com/siddhantvinchurkar/api-ai-facebook/" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.</p>
									<ul class="actions">
										<li><a href="#mooru" class="button scrolly">More downstairs &darr;</a></li>
									</ul>
								</div>
							</div>
