							<div class="content">
								<div class="inner">
									<h2><a href="https://api.ai/" target="_blank">The Platform</a></h2>
									<p>For those who wonder, Onyx is built on <a href="https://api.ai/" target="_blank">API.AI</a> and this is what allows onyx to be truly omnipresent. You can experience Onyx in her raw form <a href="https://bot.api.ai/onyx" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>
