							<h2>Get in touch</h2>
							<p>Be it to tell us how great Onyx is or how poorly she functions; we, the developers, love to hear from you. We value your feedback more than Romeo valued Juliet. This is because your feedback helps us make our creations better, which is something we strive for. You can text, call or email us. You can even choose to write us a letter if you feel romantic. Don't worry, unlike the NSA, we respect your privacy and your feedback will remain confidential until such a time when Johnny Depp stops playing with his barbies.</p>
